data.description: Back on the market, Sadly down payment assistance was denied. Property easily appraised at full price. Won't last long at this amazing price.. Sitting on over 1/2 an acre. with preserve on one side is almost impossible to find here.  This Cracker home(not Modular)  with expensive cedar siding helps keep you pest free. It  features a wood burning fireplace in the  family room. A spring fed pond in the back yard and plenty room to store that boat or RV on your own  private lot located in  desirable Aripeka .Enjoy deer and other wildlife living on private dead-end road named after original owner. Amazingly you will get to enjoy the tranquility of seclusion, yet ironically be super close great amenities .Bridge fishing, kayaking. Super close boat ramp and a general store within a  5 minute walk .Sun West or Spring Hill  Shopping all less than 10 minutes away. . Laundry area in screened lanai, but can be moved easily inside as hookups are in back corner of large pantry storage off kitchen. Screened lanai also features an outdoor shower. Lanai leads into separate  Sun room. Property has NEVER flooded 7ft. above sea level. Elevation report available. Has potential with some updates to give you instant equity. Book your appointment today! Sold "As- Is".
